        "id": 5085
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-05-21T13:50:58Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "We consider it a success if there was nothing to submit? I guess had the caller provided semaphores to the flush then they would have been submitted? Slightly wondering if the result should be tri-state: success, nothing to do, failure. But maybe that\u0027s overthinking it.",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 56,
        "startChar": 30,
        "endLine": 56,
        "endChar": 46
      },
      "revId": "b218722596fd41b31acf4db2d7a328f358d79ada",
